<div style="padding:10px 20px 10px 0px;" class="post"><b>Architecture's Second Life<br />
(in two acts)</b><br />
<br />
<b>Cast, in order of appearance:</b><br />
<a href="http://archinect.com/members/profile_view_ind.php?id=8857" target="_blank"><b>Heather Ring</b></a><br />
<a href="http://archinect.com/members/profile_view_ind.php?id=601" target="_blank"><b>Bryan Boyer</b></a><br />
<a href="http://www.international-festival.org/" target="_blank"><b>Tor Lindstrand</b></a><br />
<a href="http://www.unrealstockholm.org/wiki/index.php?title=Main_Page" target="_blank"><b>LOL Architects</b></a><br />
