<div class="comments" style="padding: 0px 20px 10px 0px;">Posted by: <a href="http://www.archinect.com/members/profile_view_ind.php?id=13458">Orhan Ayyce</a> on Feb 02, 07 | 8:06 pm</div>

</div><div style="padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px; border-bottom: 1px dashed #C7C2BE;">

<div class="comments" style="padding: 0px 20px 5px 0px;">As seen in the News Section:<br />
